# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s2_mei.rpy:13
translate english ch1_s2_mei_58aeceaa:

    # tester "下一个，萧媚！"
    tester "Next, Xiao Mei!"

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s2_mei.rpy:18
translate english ch1_s2_mei_37eb54a2:

    # "听着测验人的喊声，一名少女快速的人群中跑出，少女刚刚出场，附近的议论声便是小了许多，一双双略微火热的目光，牢牢的锁定着少女的脸颊……"
    "Hearing the tester's shout, a young girl quickly ran out from the crowd. As soon as she appeared, the surrounding chatter quieted down significantly, and pairs of slightly fiery gazes locked firmly onto her cheeks..."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s2_mei.rpy:20
translate english ch1_s2_mei_0d602913:

    # "少女年龄不过十四左右，虽然并算不上绝色，不过那张稚气未脱的小脸，却是蕴含着淡淡的妩媚，清纯与妩媚，矛盾的集合，让得她成功的成为了全场瞩目的焦点……"
    "The girl was only about fourteen years old. Although not a peerless beauty, her childish face contained a faint charm. The contradictory combination of purity and charm successfully made her the focus of the entire field..."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s2_mei.rpy:25
translate english ch1_s2_mei_0101399b:

    # "少女快步上前，小手轻车熟路的触摸着漆黑的魔石碑，然后缓缓闭上眼睛……"
    "The girl walked up quickly, her small hand deftly touching the pitch-black Magic Testing Monolith, then slowly closed her eyes..."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s2_mei.rpy:30
translate english ch1_s2_mei_bc60a693:

    # "在少女闭眼片刻之后，漆黑的魔石碑之上再次亮起了光芒……"
    "Moments after the girl closed her eyes, light shone once again on the pitch-black Magic Testing Monolith..."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s2_mei.rpy:32
translate english ch1_s2_mei_7f8991e5:

    # tester "斗之气：七段！"
    tester "Dou Qi: 7th Stage!"

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s2_mei.rpy:34
translate english ch1_s2_mei_1247d80e:

    # tester "萧媚，斗之气：七段！级别：高级！"
    tester "Xiao Mei, Dou Qi: 7th Stage! Rank: High!"

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s2_mei.rpy:39
translate english ch1_s2_mei_30070b1f:

    # xm "耶！"
    xm "Yay!"

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s2_mei.rpy:41
translate english ch1_s2_mei_07b7dd65:

    # "听着测验员所喊出的成绩，少女脸颊扬起了得意的笑容……"
    "Hearing the result shouted by the tester, a proud smile rose on the girl's cheeks..."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s2_mei.rpy:46
translate english ch1_s2_mei_b5e12477:

    # crowd "啧啧，七段斗之气，真了不起，按这进度，恐怕顶多只需要三年时间，她就能称为一名真正的斗者了吧……"
    crowd "Tsk tsk, 7th Stage Dou Qi, truly impressive. At this rate, perhaps in at most three years, she will be able to become a true Dou Practitioner..."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s2_mei.rpy:48
translate english ch1_s2_mei_6a53cdb9:

    # crowd "不愧是家族中种子级别的人物啊……"
    crowd "Worthy of being a seed-level figure in the clan..."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s2_mei.rpy:50
translate english ch1_s2_mei_4ee6345f:

    # "听着人群中传来的一阵阵羡慕声，少女脸颊上的笑容更是多了几分，虚荣心，这是很多女孩都无法抗拒的诱惑……"
    "Hearing the waves of envy from the crowd, the smile on the girl's face deepened. Vanity is a temptation that few girls can resist..."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s2_mei.rpy:55
translate english ch1_s2_mei_850b3a23:

    # "与平日里的几个姐妹互相笑谈着，萧媚的视线，忽然的透过周围的人群，停在了人群外的那一道孤单身影上……"
    "Chatting and laughing with her usual sisters, Xiao Mei's gaze suddenly pierced through the surrounding crowd and stopped on that lonely figure outside the crowd..."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s2_mei.rpy:57
translate english ch1_s2_mei_7341f9bd:

    # "皱眉思虑了瞬间，萧媚还是打消了过去的念头，现在的两人，已经不在同一个阶层之上，以萧炎最近几年的表现，成年后，顶多只能作为家族中的下层人员，而天赋优秀的她，则将会成为家族重点培养的强者，前途可以说是不可限量。"
    "Frowning and pondering for a moment, Xiao Mei dismissed the idea of going over. The two of them were no longer on the same level. Given Xiao Yan's performance in recent years, after coming of age, he would at most be a lower-level member of the clan. Meanwhile, she, with her excellent talent, would become a powerhouse heavily cultivated by the clan, her future limitless."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s2_mei.rpy:59
translate english ch1_s2_mei_c19f33c7:

    # xm "唉……"
    xm "Sigh..."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s2_mei.rpy:61
translate english ch1_s2_mei_d4e52bad:

    # "莫名的轻叹了一口气，萧媚脑中忽然浮现出三年前那意气风发的少年，四岁练气，十岁拥有九段斗之气，十一岁突破十段斗之气，成功凝聚斗之气旋，一跃成为家族百年之内最年轻的斗者！"
    "Sighing inexplicably, Xiao Mei suddenly recalled the high-spirited boy from three years ago. Starting Dou Qi training at four, possessing 9th Stage Dou Qi at ten, breaking through 10th Stage Dou Qi at eleven, successfully condensing a Dou Qi Cyclone, and instantly becoming the youngest Dou Practitioner in the clan in a century!"

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s2_mei.rpy:68
translate english ch1_s2_mei_6fea3bd5:

    # "当初的少年，自信而且潜力无可估量，不知让得多少少女对其春心荡漾，当然，这也包括以前的萧媚。"
    "The boy back then was confident and had immeasurable potential. Who knows how many girls' hearts fluttered for him, and of course, that included the former Xiao Mei."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s2_mei.rpy:70
translate english ch1_s2_mei_8f076bae:

    # "然而天才的道路，貌似总是曲折的，三年之前，这名声望达到巅峰的天才少年，却是突兀的接受到了有生以来最残酷的打击，不仅辛辛苦苦修炼十数载方才凝聚的斗之气旋，一夜之间，化为乌有，而且体内的斗之气，也是随着时间的流逝，变得诡异的越来越少。"
    "However, the path of a genius seems always tortuous. Three years ago, this genius boy, whose fame had reached its peak, suddenly received the cruelest blow of his life. Not only did the Dou Qi Cyclone, which he had painstakingly cultivated for over a decade, vanish overnight, but the Dou Qi in his body also strangely decreased as time passed."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s2_mei.rpy:72
translate english ch1_s2_mei_01fbbf27:

    # "斗之气消失的直接结果，便是导致其实力不断的后退。"
    "The direct result of the disappearance of Dou Qi was the continuous regression of his strength."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s2_mei.rpy:74
translate english ch1_s2_mei_58ffb929:

    # "从天才的神坛，一夜跌落到了连普通人都不如的地步，这种打击，让得少年从此失魂落魄，天才之名，也是逐渐的被不屑与嘲讽所替代。"
    "Falling from the altar of a genius overnight to a state worse than an ordinary person, this blow left the boy despondent ever since. The title of genius was gradually replaced by disdain and ridicule."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s2_mei.rpy:76
translate english ch1_s2_mei_a3bffa8a:

    # "站的越高，摔得越狠，这次的跌落，或许就再也没有爬起的机会。"
    "The higher you stand, the harder you fall. This fall, perhaps there will never be a chance to get up again."
